  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for supporting alignment between climate risk and climate impact in finance portfolios&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;Conveners.org will convene actors working on both climate financial risk and climate financial impact. The goal is to bridge the two sides, linking risk and impact in a more actionable way for banks and asset owners/managers. They will convene leaders working to decarbonize financial portfolios in an effort to bridge the gap, and unify efforts between, the impact-focused and risk-management focused lenses of the community.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
